  "_notes": [
    "Baseline 17e4940625388c7b893b6f3cb0bff43977da5a5f is the microsoft/vcpkg commit",
    "'[dawn] Update to 20260410.140140 [skia] Update to 148 (#51241)' dated 2026-04-20.",
    "At that baseline, port 'dawn' resolves to google/dawn tag v20260410.140140 ",
    "(commit 493241c40dc94ca283c5e2b42a03911df870f359). Pinning here so every",
    "builder, harness run, and CI job uses the same Dawn ABI, regardless of when",
    "vcpkg is re-bootstrapped.",
    "Symbols relied on at this pin (verified against src/dawn/dawn.json at the",
    "Dawn tag):",
    "  WGPUStringView, WGPUCallbackMode_AllowProcessEvents,",
    "  WGPURequestAdapterCallbackInfo, WGPURequestDeviceCallbackInfo,",
    "  WGPUSurfaceSourceWindowsHWND (note: legacy *DescriptorFromWindowsHWND",
    "    no longer exists at this pin — use Source name),",
    "  WGPUSType_SurfaceSourceWindowsHWND,",
    "  wgpuInstanceProcessEvents, wgpuInstanceCreateSurface,",
    "  wgpuSurfaceConfigure/GetCapabilities/GetCurrentTexture/Present/Unconfigure,",
    "  wgpuAdapterGetInfo/GetLimits/GetFeatures, wgpuDeviceGetLimits/GetFeatures,",
    "  wgpuBufferMapAsync (new callbackInfo signature),",
    "  wgpuDevicePushErrorScope/PopErrorScope,",
    "  wgpuAdapterInfoFreeMembers, wgpuSupportedFeaturesFreeMembers,",
    "  wgpuSurfaceCapabilitiesFreeMembers.",
    "Symbols that do NOT exist at this pin (removed or never present):",
    "  wgpuDeviceSetUncapturedErrorCallback — use WGPUDeviceDescriptor.",
    "    uncapturedErrorCallbackInfo at device creation time.",
    "  WGPUSurfaceDescriptorFromWindowsHWND / WGPUSType_SurfaceDescriptorFromWindowsHWND",
    "    — renamed to WGPUSurfaceSourceWindowsHWND / ..._SurfaceSourceWindowsHWND."
  ]
